{
  "name": "peft-from-scratch",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "type": "module",
  "description": "从零用 TypeScript 手写 LoRA / QLoRA / Adapter / Prefix-Tuning。纯算法、离线 CPU 可跑、种子确定可复现。配套书库《高效微调 PEFT 从零》。",
